title: Marble Moments

creator: Tom Brückner
descriptionHtml:
Marble Moments is an augmented reality app that allows you to drop memories wherever they originated, creating a world that blends the physical environment with digital moments.

It allows you to capture your favorite experiences, like a concert, a hike, or a cherished family memory, in the form of digital capsules. From then on, that memory will live forever for anyone who comes back to that location. Your Marbles can be shared with your friends, the world, or kept private.

Make your precious moments infinite. Download Marble Memories now and start painting the world with the story of your life.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: This is our brand-new, completely redesigned Marble 2.0. We're sure you'll love it!

title: Marble Moments

creator: Tom Brückner
descriptionHtml:
Dive into a world full of memories and stories, and re-experience them right where they happened!

Kids grow up, parties fade out, roadtrips end, but memories stay. Marble allows you to conserve your most valuable moments, coolest happenings and most magnificent stories - and to share them with your loved ones, the world, or to keep them private. Each memory get's what you think it deserves.

Enable your favorite moments to be relived instead of just remembered. Download Marble Moments today!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Bug fixes and performance improvements.

title: Marbleverse

creator: Tom Brückner
descriptionHtml:
Build your own metaverse in the real world.

REVEAL THE MARBLEVERSE
· The Marbleverse is an Augmented Reality Metaverse.
· The app uses your camera to reveal marbles all around you.

DROP MARBLES
· A “Marble” is a virtual container for digital content.
· The app opens right to your camera so you can quickly record a video and post it in a marble!
· Marbles exist in physical locations for other users to discover.
· Post photos and videos in marbles to leave a trail of memories.

FACEMASKS
· Flip to the front camera and express yourself with facemasks!

INFO MARBLES
· Discover thousands of Info Marbles, such as Wikipedia Marbles and Metro Marbles, that contain useful information about your location.

LAYERS
· Create public layers that work like hashtags to build communities.
· Create private groups where Marbles are only visible to you and your friends.

CHAT
· Message users directly through live messaging within the app.

NFT HUNT
· Earn NFTs by discovering NFT marbles.

TAP MAP
· View public marbles all over the world by using the Tap Map.

TOURS
· Create tours in the Marbleverse for users to follow at any time.

RADAR
· Use the radar to view the location of Marbles near you.

FEED
· See the latest marbles dropped by users you follow in your feed.

NOTE: Marbleverse is based on GPS and Augmented Reality so be sure to enable location and camera access to start.
descriptionShort: Build your own metaverse in the real world.
